snippet.title: Microsoft Power Platform
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Microsoft Power Platform YouTube channel.

If you'd like to keep up to date with everything from across the Microsoft Power Platform Community and beyond, feel free to subscribe to our channel for all the latest videos and tutorials.

For more tasty tips, why not come and join the convo in our Community here: https://aka.ms/PP_Community

And we also have a super-active LinkedIn page here: https://www.linkedin.com/company/microsoft-power-platform-community/
